entries.title_d: Recover a NDC craft from Ay'Nat pirates
entries.title: Naboo System: Duty: Recover the Captured Diplomatic Corps Transport
entries.thanks_2: This was a long day, thank you Captain
entries.thanks_1: Thank you for getting us out of there.
entries.taunt_3: I hear death in space is almost instant.  Pitty.
entries.taunt_1: If we can't have that ship, none may.
entries.target_disabled: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#00ff00 The NDC Transport has been disabled. Recovery operation will begin shortly. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.recovery_success: The NDC Transport has been secured. Good job, pilot.
entries.quest_recover_d: Pull up close to a disabled craft to initiate capture
entries.quest_escort_d: Escort the captured ship safely out of the system
entries.quest_disable_d: Target the engines to disable the target
entries.failed_escape: The transport has escaped the area under Ay'Nat. This is a disgrace! Return to base at once!
entries.failed_destroy: The transport was destroyed! This is unacceptable! Return to base at once. You are to blame for this failure!
entries.escort_wiped_out: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#00ff00 The escorting craft have been eliminated. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.complete: We've made it to safety. Jumping to lightspeed...now.
entries.capture_started: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#00ff00 Primary mission target recovery operation underway. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.capture_phase_2: Resistance eliminated. We've taken the bridge. We'll be underway shortly.
entries.capture_phase_1: Boarding party is facing light resistance.
entries.capture_complete: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#00ff00 Primary mission target recovery operation complete! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Comptuer: < \#pcontrast1 The attack has stopped. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy craft detected on attack vector. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_2: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 The NDC Transport has arrived. Disable the craft and eliminate her escort! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_1: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 The captured trasnport will arrive shortly \#pcontrast3 >
entries.abort: Roger, abort code received. Heading home...
